<font color="#FF0000">WHILE AT THE WALL</font><br>
<tt>Sat May 10 22:24:55 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
We once cluster-f***ed into a huge bunker complex. Chuck pinned us done with fire and brimstone. Gutsey six of ours called in 8&quot; and 175's right on our poz, cause Charlie had his tubes right outside of our perimeter, if you could call it that. Thought for sure I was a toe tag number that day. Trees falling all on top off us, us being tossed into the air like so much dust. Eardrums blown and bleeding. Sustained considerable KIA's and WIA's as well as a mighty fine L.T. that day, but nary a one from your guns. Took us three days to get out for Archlight to do their job. Couldn't have done it without you guys though.<br><br>
While at the Wall, you remember those that you saved that day, as well as those that died! I'm counting on you!
<p><code>-- docdel@maui.net  (Doc Del) </code><p>


